0Z","msg":"仲未明 需要驗腦？"},{"pid":"9ce53015588ce1e099accf9230041f2145bce32c","tid":1481843,"uid":264215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />see L 4 ngor"},{"pid":"d96f05c425df4b96faae537c5bdd094f49bff3a8","tid":1481843,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ce53015588ce1e099accf9230041f2145bce32c","tid":1481843,"uid":264215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />see L 4 ngor"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:44:36.000Z","msg":"see L 4 5 mo"},{"pid":"b9998b4d7311d7f28252cfb7f97bdd07d7b84377","tid":1481843,"uid":60000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:47:02.000Z","msg":"難怪香港英文退步"},{"pid":"54e3c0c7a282d6590f5e3b9c5e242e50531f9d21","tid":1481843,"uid":139409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:47:27.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnf9O7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbnf9O7G.jpg&h=5ee9af01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1NUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=42460da6\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1NUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=42460da6\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"f86eb1fd0d5b25fe7831c301d1593b8ba324270f","tid":1481843,"uid":306058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fc190981ec5a0502dda8951890fb146cc1bf76e","tid":1481843,"uid":25183,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T01:12:58.000Z","msg":"港式英語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n毛ee實激到彈起"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:48:00.000Z","msg":"毛ee睇完可能嬲過見到林奠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b5d1911a49bc3bf07d890f424ce1780dc07762